00:34:56,000 --> 00:35:00,000
 But let me go to Romans chapter 12, starting in verse 2.

489
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:04,000
 It says, "Do not conform any longer to the patterns of this world,

490
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:07,000
 but be transformed by the renewing of your mind.

491
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:15,000
 Then you will be able to test and approve what God's will is, His good, pleasing and perfect will."

492
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:17,000
 This is such a powerful verse.

493
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:21,000
 Paul's saying, "Hey, you want to get back to where things are supposed to be?

494
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:24,000
 You want to actually begin to see your emotions as they should?

495
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:26,000
 You want to be able to think in the right ways?

496
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:32,000
 Well, here, you don't have to be conformed anymore to the patterns of the world,

497
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,000
 the will of your emotions.

498
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:40,000
 You can be transformed by the renewing of your mind.

499
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:44,000
 Why? So that you can then discern," and he says this,

500
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:48,000
 "You can discern what God's perfect will is."

501
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:55,000
 I'm going to write, "The will of God, His good, pleasing and perfect will,

502
00:35:55,000 --> 00:36:01,000
 which brings your thinking, your emotions and your body, your behavior, your actions,

503
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:06,000
 all into alignment in Christlikeness."

504
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,000
 Isn't that great?

505
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:13,000
 If only we could realize that all of this is trying to define us,

506
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:17,000
 but actually it's the work of the Spirit of God that creates a space in us.

507
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:19,000
 Not that all of this is evil.

508
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:23,000
 Remember, emotions are given by God, that they are actually part of His characteristic,

509
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:25,000
 that it's not wrong for us to feel.

510
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:27,000
 It's not that we suppress all this stuff.

511
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:32,000
 It's just that we gain a fresh perspective on it through the lens of the will of God,

512
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:36,000
 which defines our thinking, defines our emotions, and defines our physicality,

513
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:42,000
 so we can then be more like Christ in the world.

514
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:47,000
 And the Bible says the ability, the thing that creates this space,

515
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:52,000
 and it helps us to understand and discern God's will, is the Spirit of God.

516
00:36:52,000 --> 00:37:02,000
 The Spirit, which is already inside of you, works to align you to the will of God,

517
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:08,000
 so you can redeem your psychology, your emotions and your physical self,

518
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:15,000
 so that this comes in alignment with this.

519
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:19,000
 That's the Bible's answer for how we then journey in our emotions.

520
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:29,000
 The Spirit of God at work in you, and that Spirit is love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness,

521
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:32,000
 faithfulness, gentleness, and the ultimate one, what's the last one?

522
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:37,000
 Self-control.

523
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:41,000
 It amazes me that God has placed inside of us the very thing

524
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:44,000
 that can bring all of this under self-mastering control.

525
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,000
 Not that all of this is evil and wrong and bad.

526
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:49,000
 There is so much good that happens inside of this.

527
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:56,000
 But if this determines and defines this, then we've got ourselves out of whack.

528
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:59,000
 And emotional exhaustion is possible.

529
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:04,000
 But when this enables this to come under self-control,

530
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:09,000
 well then we're able to live as Christ has always caused us to.

531
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:13,000
 May I encourage you to redefine your relationship with your emotions,

532
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:16,000
 so that you can bring all of it under control.

